{ And this is consistent with that aim of rapid development. With the Koltanowski variation, White immediately asks a question of Black and tries to seize the initiative, and unsurprisingly we don't agree with Yuriy Krykun in his fun 'Unleash the Bull: 1...e5' course that 'Black is somewhat better'. Far from it!   5...exd4  is very much an option too, but many  3...Bc5  players see this as a Two Knights Defence line 3...Nf6, so eschew it. We'll have plenty of coverage of  6.e5  , the Max Lange, in Theory 1B1. }
