{ This time  12.Bf6?  doesn't blunder anything, but there's just not a great move for White after the calm  12...O-O  , and if  13.Nxd6  cxd6  14.Bxd4  Bg4  , exploiting the downside to the early  h4  . As such, we should switch approach and only now go in for the central exchange. }
