{ Ultra-aggression once again from Black, and the only move tried thus far on the database.   14...d3?!  15.Re3  would favorably regain the pawn,   while after  14...O-O  15.Nxd4  Nxd4  White can either keep things simple with  16.Qxd4  or try  16.cxd4!?  Rac8  17.Qd3  Rc4  18.Rad1  followed by swinging the queen across to  g3  . }
