{ The line-closing } 3... e6
{ has been by some margin the most popular of Black's alternatives to capturing on e4. Now White can simply and sensibly go 4 Nc3, as once played by the world champion in a bullet game against Wesley So, but a central advance is more in the spirit of the Hillbilly: }
